data.name: TXIDMenuItem.ToolTipText
data.value:
Box to the right must be Green before you can Transmit a Waterfall TEXT ID or Image.
To send Text: Type in Text that fits in the Box. To Send bitmap: Type name of file with . on the end (i.e. test. for test.bmp) Must be a small 24bit grayscale image. Right Click on Call Sign Box to open Folder to place Bitmap into.
Red: Move your mouse into and out of the Text box to start creating file Green: Done creating the file the waterfall, ready to Transmit (Hit TX WaterID button) Yellow: Need to move mouse in/out of text box.
MAKE SURE WAVE OPTIONS ARE SET TO POST AUDIO for both RX & TX
